ImprovedInitiative.Creatures.gnidu18n:
{"Id":"gnidu18n","Name":"Chaos Witch Quelaag","Path":"Dark Souls","Source":"Dark Souls","Type":"Large fiend (demon), chaotic neutral","HP":{"Value":150,"Notes":"20d10+40"},"AC":{"Value":18,"Notes":""},"InitiativeModifier":2,"InitiativeAdvantage":false,"Speed":["40ft."],"Abilities":{"Str":"16","Dex":"14","Con":"14","Cha":"6","Int":"12","Wis":"16"},"DamageVulnerabilities":["lightning"],"DamageResistances":[],"DamageImmunities":["fire","poison"],"ConditionImmunities":[],"Saves":[{"Name":"Dex","Modifier":"6"},{"Name":"Wis","Modifier":"7"}],"Skills":[{"Name":"Arcana","Modifier":"5"}],"Senses":["darkvision 60ft.","passive Perception 13"],"Languages":["Common","Infernal"],"Challenge":"9 (5000 XP)","Traits":[{"Name":"Fury Sword.","Content":"When Quelaag makes an attack with her sword, she deals an additional 6d6 fire damage. (included in attack)","Usage":""}],"Actions":[{"Name":"Multiattack.","Content":"Quelaag makes one sword attack and one bite attack.","Usage":""},{"Name":"Sword.","Content":"Melee Weapon Attack: +7 to hit, reach 5ft. Hit: 7 (1d8+3) slashing damage + 21 (6d6) fire damage","Usage":""},{"Name":"Bite.","Content":"Melee Weapon Attack: +7 to hit, reach 5ft. hit: 10 (2d6+3) piercing damage.","Usage":""},{"Name":"Lava Discharge (Recharge 5-6).","Content":"Quelaag's spider mouth spits out lava in a 15ft. cone. Each creature in the cone must make a DC 15 Dexterity saving throw, taking 28 (8d6) fire damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one.","Usage":""},{"Name":"Heat Pulse (Recharge 5-6).","Content":"Quelaag radiates an intense heat from her body, damaging everything around her. Creatures within 10ft. of Quelaag must make a DC 15 Constitution saving throw, taking 27 (6d8) fire damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one.","Usage":""}],"Reactions":[],"LegendaryActions":[],"Description":"The torso and head of a beautiful human woman conjoined at the hip with a terrifying drider. Quelaag was once a sorceress, but tampering with dangerous magic transformed her into a terrifying beast. Now, she hides herself away in a cave deep in a dangerous swamp, caring only for her similarly deformed siblings and protecting her home.

*Demonic Mutation:* Quelaag was once a beautiful human sorceress, one of the first to ever have power over fire, for both destruction and creation. The daughter of hte Withc of Izaleth, an all-powerful sorceress, she and her sisters maintained dominion over their kingdom with their incredible magic. However, during an attempt to recreate the First Flame, an incredible source of magical power, they released a terrifying, demonic power that transformed Quelaag and her family into demons.

*Fury Sword:* constructed of her own soul, Quelaag brandishes a black, curved sword swathed in flames. Legendary for its deadliness, few have withstood the heat of the blade and survived.","Player":"","Version":"1.6.4","ImageURL":"https://pre00.deviantart.net/aa85/th/pre/i/2015/169/8/1/chaos_witch_quelaag_by_uselessappendage-d8xuhzl.png"}

