{"Id":"iq2gbrkg","Name":"Yan-C-Bin","Source":"","Type":"H elemental, elemental evil, neutral evil","HP":{"Value":283,"Notes":"(21d12+147)"},"AC":{"Value":22,"Notes":"(natural armor)"},"InitiativeModifier":0,"Speed":["50 ft.","fly 150 ft."],"Abilities":{"Str":18,"Dex":24,"Con":24,"Int":16,"Wis":21,"Cha":23},"DamageVulnerabilities":[],"DamageResistances":["cold","fire;  bludgeoning","piercing","and slashing from nonmagical weapons"],"DamageImmunities":["lightning","poison","thunder"],"ConditionImmunities":["charmed","frightened","paralyzed","petrified","poisoned","prone","restrained"],"Saves":[{"Name":"Dex","Modifier":13},{"Name":"Wis","Modifier":11},{"Name":"Cha","Modifier":12}],"Skills":[],"Senses":["blindsight 120 ft."],"Languages":["Auran"],"Challenge":"18","Traits":[{"Name":"Air Form","Content":"Yan-C-Bin can enter a hostile creature's space and stop there. He can move through a space as narrow as 1 inch wide without squeezing if air could pass through that space.","Usage":""},{"Name":"Empowered Attacks","Content":"Yan-C-Bin's slam attacks are treated as magical for the purpose of bypassing resistance and immunity to nonmagical weapons.","Usage":""},{"Name":"Innate Spellcasting","Content":"Yan-C-Bin's innate spellcasting ability is Charisma (spell save DC 20, +12 to hit with spell attacks). He can innately cast the following spells, requiring no material components: 

• At will: gust of wind, invisibility, lightning bolt
• 2/day each: chain lightning, cloudkill, haste","Usage":""},{"Name":"Legendary Resistance (3/Day)","Content":"If Yan-C-Bin fails a saving throw, he can choose to succeed instead.","Usage":""},{"Name":"Magic Resistance","Content":"Yan-C-Bin has advantage on saving throws against spells and other magical effects.","Usage":""}],"Actions":[{"Name":"Multiattack","Content":"Yan-C-Bin makes two slam attacks.","Usage":""},{"Name":"Slam","Content":"Melee Weapon Attack: +14 to hit, reach 10 ft., one target. Hit: 20 (3d8 + 7) force damage plus 10 (3d6) lightning damage.","Usage":""},{"Name":"Thundercrack (Recharges after a Short or Long Rest)","Content":"Yan-C-Bin unleashes a terrible thundercrack in a 100-foot- radius sphere centered on himself. All other creatures in the area must succeed on a DC 24 Constitution saving throw or take 31 (9d6) thunder damage and be deafened for 1 minute. On a successful save, a creature takes half as much damage and is deafened until the start of Yan-C-Bin's next turn.","Usage":""},{"Name":"Change Shape","Content":"Yan-C-Bin polymorphs into a Medium humanoid. While in polymorphed form, a swirling breeze surrounds him, his eyes are pale and cloudy, and he loses the Air Form trait. He can remain in polymorphed form for up to 1 hour. Reverting to his true form requires an action.","Usage":""},{"Name":"Summon Elementals (1/Day)","Content":"Yan-C-Bin summons up to three air elementals and loses 30 hit points for each elemental he summons. Summoned elementals have maximum hit points, appear within 100 feet of Yan-C-Bin, and disappear if Yan-C-Bin is reduced to 0 hit points.","Usage":""}],"Reactions":[],"LegendaryActions":[{"Name":"Peal of Thunder","Content":"Yan-C-Bin unleashes a peal of thunder that can be heard out to a range of 300 feet. Each creature within 30 feet of Yan-C-Bin takes 5 (1d10) thunder damage.","Usage":""},{"Name":"Teleport (Costs 2 Actions)","Content":"Yan-C-Bin magically teleports up to 120 feet to an unoccupied space he can see. Anything Yan-C-Bin is wearing or carrying is teleported with him.","Usage":""},{"Name":"Suffocate (Costs 3 Actions)","Content":"Yan-C-Bin steals the air of one breathing creature he can see within 60 feet of him. The target must make a DC 21 Constitution saving throw. On a failed save, the target drops to 0 hit points and is dying. On a successful save, the target can't breathe or speak until the start of its next turn.","Usage":""}],"Description":"","Player":""}
